## Known bug fixed in PR #162

`coach-board.ts` line ~2918 used to unconditionally overwrite every template player's `angle` with the team default:

```typescript
// ❌ Before — ignores template angles
angle: playerAngle(p.team)

// ✅ After — respects explicitly set template angles
angle: p.angle ?? playerAngle(p.team)
```

This caused every rondo outer player to face right (Team A default = 90°) regardless of the angle set in the template. The fix uses `??` so that only players without an explicit angle fall back to the team default. Do not revert this change.
